						<summary>

						<p>Lintel of the <hi rend="italic">garbhagriha</hi> of the Kēśavasvāmi temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">1067 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It registers a grant of land and a garden for the worship and offerings to the God Śrī Vishṇudēva the image of which got prepared and installed by <hi rend="italic">perggaḍe</hi> Kōsanamayya.</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka 988, Parābhava, Phālguṇa, Śu. 13, Thursday corresponding to 1067 A.D., March 1.</p>						

						</summary>
